    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[提高百度云下载速度]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2017/01/02/%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%91%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>百度云对下载速度进行了限制，为了提高下载速度可以使用<a href="https://github.com/GangZhuo/BaiduPCS" target="_blank" rel="external">BaiduPcs</a>工具进行下载。<br>以下是Mac下安装该软看，具体可以参考帮助文档</p>
<h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><p>如果没有安装openssl的话需要安装openssl</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">brew install openssl</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>如果已经安装过的话直接下面步骤</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">git clone git@github.com:GangZhuo/BaiduPCS.git</div><div class="line">cd BaiduPCS</div><div class="line">make</div><div class="line">make install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h3><p>下载之前设置下线程数目</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">pcs set --max_thread=&quot;10&quot;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>使用pcs login命令登陆</li>
<li>使用pcs cd 进入具体目录</li>
<li>使用pcs download &lt;远程文件名&gt; &lt;本地文件名&gt; 进行下载</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[Mac使用技巧]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/12/31/Mac%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在自己的hp的电脑上搞了个黑苹果，自此开始了自己的Mac之旅。使用了一段时间了，遇到了不少的问题，该文章用于记录自己使用过程中遇到的一些问题和解决方法。</p>
<h3 id="关机不断电问题"><a href="#关机不断电问题" class="headerlink" title="关机不断电问题"></a>关机不断电问题</h3><p>黑苹果很可能会出现关机不断电的问题，主要可能是电池的驱动和usb3.0的问题。在我的电脑上，电源驱动已经原生驱动，主要问题可能是usb3.0引起的，为了解决方法可以禁用掉usb3.0，也可以选择别的接口插入usb设备。另外还要注意，黑苹果下关机后电源指示灯熄灭需要有一定的时间，不是关机黑屏后会立马熄灭，不要着急强按电源键。</p>
<h3 id="如何使用360wifi"><a href="#如何使用360wifi" class="headerlink" title="如何使用360wifi"></a>如何使用360wifi</h3><p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1gfhuAGV" target="_blank" rel="external">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1gfhuAGV</a><br>下载驱动，用<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1kUSZtiv" target="_blank" rel="external">kext utility</a>进行安装，安装完成后重启电脑。另外需要安装<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1jI7CUTg" target="_blank" rel="external">wireless utility</a>。注意，由于不是使用的原生驱动，升级系统之后会丢失，需要再次安装。</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[bootstrap学习笔记]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/12/30/bootstrap%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><link href="//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"></p>
<script src="//cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>




<p>用了一段时间的bootstrap了，觉得得写点什么，不然过段时间之后就又会忘记得差不多了。bootstrap框架主要包含了一些快速开发的css和js组件。</p>
<h3 id="引入bootstrap库"><a href="#引入bootstrap库" class="headerlink" title="引入bootstrap库"></a>引入bootstrap库</h3><p>为了提高速度，最好采用CDN的bootstrap，jquery需要在bootstrap之前引入，否则可能会出现问题。</p>
<figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">&lt;link href=<span class="string">"//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css"</span> rel=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span>&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src="//cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/3.1.1/jquery.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div><div class="line">&lt;script src=<span class="string">"//cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.js"</span>&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<button class="btn btn-danger">button</button>

<h3 id="媒体查询"><a href="#媒体查询" class="headerlink" title="媒体查询"></a>媒体查询</h3><p>bootstrap使用了媒体查询来实现响应式布局，比如对于container，针对不同的设备宽度可以进行不同的css设置</p>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">576px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.container</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">540px</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">100%</span>;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">768px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.container</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">720px</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">100%</span>;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">992px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.container</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">960px</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">100%</span>;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">1200px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.container</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">width</span>: <span class="number">1140px</span>;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">max-width</span>: <span class="number">100%</span>;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>bootstrap主要定义了以下几个分辨率切换点</p>
<ul>
<li>576</li>
<li>768</li>
<li>960</li>
<li>1200</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="网格系统"><a href="#网格系统" class="headerlink" title="网格系统"></a>网格系统</h3><p>bootstrap使用了叫做grid的网格系统来进行布局。网格的使用主要是：container -&gt; row -&gt; col。 要使用网格系统，首先必须添加一个class为container或者container-fluid的html元素.  </p>
<h4 id="container"><a href="#container" class="headerlink" title="container"></a>container</h4><ul>
<li>定义了15px的左右padding</li>
<li>根据不通的屏幕尺寸，定义了container的width</li>
<li>自动container的width，剩余宽度自动左右平均margin</li>
<li>定义了最大width为100%，这样容器不会超过viewport的大小</li>
<li>另外针对不同的parent，有特殊的定制</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="container-fluid"><a href="#container-fluid" class="headerlink" title="container-fluid"></a>container-fluid</h4><ul>
<li>定义了15px的左右padding</li>
<li>相对布局</li>
<li>左右自动的margin,基本回占满viewport</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="row"><a href="#row" class="headerlink" title="row"></a>row</h4><ul>
<li>定义了左右-15px的margin，消除掉container中的15px的padding</li>
<li>bootstrap v4中使用的flex布局</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.row</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: -webkit-box;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: -webkit-flex;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: -ms-flexbox;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: flex;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">-webkit-flex-wrap</span>: wrap;</div><div class="line">      <span class="attribute">-ms-flex-wrap</span>: wrap;</div><div class="line">          <span class="attribute">flex-wrap</span>: wrap;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-right</span>: -<span class="number">15px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-left</span>: -<span class="number">15px</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="col"><a href="#col" class="headerlink" title="col"></a>col</h4><ul>
<li>bootstrap默认定义了12列，这样可以方便的支持等分成2列，3列，4列，用户根据需要可以自己改变默认方式自己定制</li>
<li>bootstrap给不同的屏幕尺寸定义了不同的col class<ul>
<li>col-xs</li>
<li>col-sm</li>
<li>col-md</li>
<li>col-lg</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>col-[xs,sm,md,lg]-[1,12]提供了相对布局，15px的左右padding，左浮动</li>
<li>使用媒体查询，根据不同的viewport大小，将有不同类型的col-[xs,sm,md,lg]生效<ul>
<li>col-xs: &lt; 768px  手机</li>
<li>col-sm: &gt; 768px  平板</li>
<li>col-md: &gt; 992px  桌面显示器</li>
<li>col-lg: &gt; 1200px 大桌面显示器</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>bootstrap的grid在不同分辨率上的行为<br><img src="http://p1.bqimg.com/567571/76676867f16a93e7.png" alt=""></li>
<li>col-[xs,sm,md,lg]-push-[1..12]<ul>
<li>定义列的左侧位置</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-push-1</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">left</span>: <span class="number">8.33333333%</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-push-0</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">left</span>: auto;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li>col-[xs,sm,md,lg]-offset-[1..12]<ul>
<li>定义列的margin-left</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-offset-1</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-left</span>: <span class="number">8.33333333%</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-offset-0</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-left</span>: <span class="number">0</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">```	 </div><div class="line">* <span class="selector-tag">col-</span><span class="selector-attr">[xs,sm,md,lg]</span><span class="selector-tag">-pull-</span><span class="selector-attr">[1..12]</span></div><div class="line">	* 定义了列的右侧位置</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">```<span class="selector-tag">css</span></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-pull-1</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">right</span>: <span class="number">8.33333333%</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.col-xs-pull-0</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">right</span>: auto;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="排版"><a href="#排版" class="headerlink" title="排版"></a>排版</h3><h4 id="标题-h1-h2-h3-h4-h5-h6"><a href="#标题-h1-h2-h3-h4-h5-h6" class="headerlink" title="标题 h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6"></a>标题 h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6</h4><ul>
<li>h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6</li>
<li>.h1, .h2, .h3, .h4, .h5, .h6</li>
<li>36px, 30px, 24px, 18px, 12px</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="副标题-small"><a href="#副标题-small" class="headerlink" title="副标题 small"></a>副标题 small</h4><ul>
<li>颜色 #777</li>
<li>h1,h2,h3 margin-top 20px, margin-bottom 10px</li>
<li>h4,h5,h6 margin-top 10px, margin-bottom 10px</li>
<li>h1,h2,h3对应的small的font-size为65%</li>
<li>h4,h5,h6对应的small的font-size为75%</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="页面主体与段落-body-p"><a href="#页面主体与段落-body-p" class="headerlink" title="页面主体与段落 body p"></a>页面主体与段落 body p</h4><ul>
<li>颜色#333，背景色#fff</li>
<li>字体大小14px</li>
<li>行高1.43</li>
<li>p元素被额外赋予了1/2行高的底边距（10px）</li>
<li>lead用于突出显示段落，调大了默认的字体和下补白</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.lead</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-bottom</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">16px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-weight</span>: <span class="number">300</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">1.4</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">768px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.lead</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">21px</span>;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><h4 id="内联文本元素"><a href="#内联文本元素" class="headerlink" title="内联文本元素"></a>内联文本元素</h4><h5 id="标记-高亮-mark"><a href="#标记-高亮-mark" class="headerlink" title="标记 高亮 mark"></a>标记 高亮 mark</h5><p>mark元素用于高亮显示文本，更改了背景色和前景色已经padding</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">mark</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#000</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: <span class="number">#ff0</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">mark</span>,</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.mark</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">padding</span>: .<span class="number">2em</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">background-color</span>: <span class="number">#fcf8e3</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>this is a <mark>mark</mark></p>
<h3 id="导航"><a href="#导航" class="headerlink" title="导航"></a>导航</h3><h4 id="navbar"><a href="#navbar" class="headerlink" title="navbar"></a>navbar</h4><pre><code>* display: none
* 相对布局
* 最小高度50px
* 下补足20px
</code></pre><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: none;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">position</span>: relative;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">min-height</span>: <span class="number">50px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">margin-bottom</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">border</span>: <span class="number">1px</span> solid transparent;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="navbar-header"><a href="#navbar-header" class="headerlink" title="navbar-header"></a>navbar-header</h4><pre><code>* 大于768px时左浮动
</code></pre><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> (min-width: <span class="number">768px</span>) &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="selector-class">.navbar-header</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">    <span class="attribute">float</span>: left;</div><div class="line">  &#125;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="navbar-brand"><a href="#navbar-brand" class="headerlink" title="navbar-brand"></a>navbar-brand</h4><ul>
<li>左浮动</li>
<li>50px高度</li>
<li>15px padding</li>
<li>18px字体以及20px行高</li>
<li>子img块状显示</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar-brand</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">float</span>: left;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">height</span>: <span class="number">50px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">padding</span>: <span class="number">15px</span> <span class="number">15px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">18px</span>;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">line-height</span>: <span class="number">20px</span>;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar-brand</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:hover</span>,</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar-brand</span><span class="selector-pseudo">:focus</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">text-decoration</span>: none;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"><span class="selector-class">.navbar-brand</span> &gt; <span class="selector-tag">img</span> &#123;</div><div class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span>: block;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="collapse"><a href="#collapse" class="headerlink" title="collapse"></a>collapse</h4><ul>
<li>用于显示和隐藏可折叠内容</li>
<li>使用<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>或者<code>&lt;button&gt;</code>添加作为折叠按钮</li>
<li>添加<mark>data-toggle=”collapse”</mark></li>
<li>添加 <mark>data-target=“#id”</mark>来指定折叠内容</li>
<li>对于<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>可以使用href代替data-target指定折叠内容</li>
<li>对于需要折叠的内容添加”collapse” class<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"container"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"row"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"#collapse-id"</span> <span class="attr">data-toggle</span>=<span class="string">"collapse"</span>&gt;</span>collapse<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"collapse-id"</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"collapse"</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">			Content that can be collapsed</div><div class="line">		<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">	<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line">   <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span>	</div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="container"><br>   <div class="row"><br>   <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1"><br>        <a href="#collapse-id" data-toggle="collapse">collapse</a><br>        <div id="collapse-id" class="collapse"><br>            Content that can be collapsed<br>        </div><br>    </div><br>   </div><br></div>
]]></content>
